title: The Great Bongo Heist
description: The boys forget to get Chata a gift for Abuela Day and in a panicked move, they pretend that the bongo drums they borrowed from Xochi are for her. Knowing they have to return the drums, Victor & Valentino pretend to be burglars to steal the bongos back.

title: Trans Oceanic Magical Cruise
description: It's fun on the high seas as the Titans enjoy a cruise filled with dangerous missions, fast cars, and alien attacks.

title: Enfrenta Tus Miedos
description: Atrapados en una tienda de mascotas, Manzana y Cebollín deben enfrentarse a sus miedos para poder evitar que Papa Frita se enfrente a los suyos.

title: Slow Love
description: A lonely snail lookin' for love literally crashes into the treehouse and asks Finn and Jake for help. Now, our heroes must teach this snail how to get a girlfriend before he destroys their home!

title: The Trouble with Truth
description: The JLA find themselves in danger of losing Wonder Woman when the goddess Athena comes to Earth with an offer Diana can't refuse, filling the position of the Goddess of Truth on Mt. Olympus.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Drawn to Sports with Zachary
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Zachary loves competing and developing his skills in karate.

title: Thick as Thieves
description: Phil the Pilferer robs Vambre and Prohyas of their very best Magiswords so he can snag the Sheepy Mantis, but the Warriors find out that no Magisword is lame as they manage to keep Phil from becoming Thief of the Year.

title: Bubble Buddies
description: Steven looks like a hero when he forms a magic crystal bubble around himself to protect a girl he likes from danger, but then panics when he can't figure out how to turn the bubble off!

title: Miedo a los Titeres
description: Mao Mao le teme a los títeres.

title: Mama a la Orden
description: Con el deseo de tener la experiencia de una madre, los osos usan una aplicación que les traerá una madre a la puerta de sus casas.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Would You Like to Enter Prime Empire?
description: While investigating a heist, the ninja discover Prime Empire, a legendary unreleased arcade game that suddenly takes control of all other games in Ninjago.

title: Felonious Prose
description: The Warrior mission of finding a lost contact lens gets seriously compromised from Vambre's obsession with the latest Veronica Victorious novel.

title: Creative Geniuses
description: The Titans visit the Jump City Comic Book Con where they meet Marv Wolfman and George Pérez, but also tangle with Control Freak over an exclusive toy.

title: El consejo del Arroyo
description: El juego del circulo siembra el caos en el Arroyo, así que Craig forma un consejo para restaurar el orden.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: While You Were Away
description: Dr. Psychobos and Princess Attea have invaded Rook's home planet Revonnah with an army of Incurseans! (Introducing new Ben alien, Astrodactyl.)

title: Escandalosos
description: Los Osos bebé se inscriben en un torneo de lucha libre mexicana.

title: ThunderDogs
description: The Thundercats agree to foster a demonic puppy from the Astral Plane until they can find it the perfect owner. But could the perfect owner be their worst enemy? Their worst enemy is Mumm-Ra in case you forgot!

title: Cowbar Jones: Origines
description: Pardo presenta la precuela de su película de Crowbar Jones a Nom Nom, con la esperanza de que acepte actuar en la película.

title: Scary Tales 2
description: It's Halloween again and the gang is desperately trying to tell the scariest story to a couple of trick or treaters. Each of the characters takes turns adding onto the last story, going through a haunted glove to a haunted action figure to haunted everything, and even a spooky song! None work in scaring the kids when suddenly a full scale alien invasion happens right before their eyes! Still, the trick or treaters are unimpressed until Richard takes the story stage and delivers a story no kid wants to hear- instead of candy, the trick or treaters would get granola bars! The kids, and Puppycorn, run away screaming.

title: We Are Heroes
description: KO struggles with his upgraded role as a member of the hero team.

title: The Bad Guy Busters
description: Izzy wants to play a superhero game and is willing to do whatever it takes to get the others to see it through.

title: Party Popper
description: Apple and Onion's party plans are interrupted by a grumpy guest.

title: Superstar Dan/Awesome Brawlers on Vacation
description: Superstar Dan: The Awesome Brawler's head to Tokyo for the Bakugan Battle League - Tokyo Edition. While Wynton, Shun, Lia and Lightning see the sites, and enjoy the tastes of Japan, Dan, as the Los Volmos Champion, has official Bakugan Battle League duties and obligations that keep him busy./Awesome Brawlers on Vacation: Lia, Lightning, Shun and Wynton explore the sights of Toyko when a rogue Bakugan shows up and rampages. The Awesome Brawlers have to spring into action, rolling out their Bakugan to stop the rogue enemy before any real damage can be done.

title: Mas del canal de todos
description: A través de otra sesión de navegación por Internet, vemos más videos subidos por los Osos y sus amigos.

title: Fragments
description: Steven heads to the woods to train with a powerful mentor.

title: Let's Meet Sonic
description: When world class hero SONIC THE HEDGEHOG visits the plaza, he teams up with KO to save the day.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: La Neblina del Paramo
description: El equipo Tennyson se hace internacional en el Omni-Copter, y la primera parada incluye una caminata por las Tierras Altas de Escocia. Pero el clima no es sólo malo, sino que hay niebla, y eso puede significa solamente una cosa: iel regreso de Niebla!

title: You Are Rad
description: When KO forgets his name tag, Rad lets him use his, which results in everyone thinking KO is Rad, including Rad himself.

title: Revienta Fiestas
description: Los planes de la fiesta de Manzana y Cebollín son interrumpidos por un invitado malhumorado.

title: I Am Okino
description: Inside one of the game zones, a Samurai named Okino faces a crisis of faith when he repeatedly fails to lead a series of Masters to victory, causing him to lose all hope, until some familiar ninja arrive.

title: Aluxes
description: When Vic finds an ancient relic that summons a gang of mischievous creatures, he uses them to do his bidding, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Wiener Club
description: Puppycorn is determined to become the Hot Dog King and joins an underground hot dog eating contest called Weiner Club. Rick warns "you are what you eat," but Puppycorn doesn't listen and eats so many hot dogs he becomes the new champion of Weiner Club. Unfortunately he also literally turns into a hot dog, that the other club members reveal they are going to eat! Unikitty and the gang now must attack with vegetables and defeat the hot dog-eating baddies in order to save the giant hot-dog-shaped Puppycorn and turn him back to normal.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Turning the Tables
description: Craig dines at the restaurant where his older brother works and orders up a plate of REVENGE... and lots of breadsticks.

title: Prank Callers
description: Mordecai and Rigby try and prank the Master Prank Caller to be the best prank callers. The MPC sends them back to 1982.

title: Tu Mundo es una Ilusion
description: K.O. intenta ayudar a un héroe en problemas y termina necesitando ayuda él también.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Yo Soy Okino
description: Dentro de una de las zonas de juego, un Samurai llamado Okino se enfrenta a una crisis de fe cuando no logra que los Maestros obtengan la victoria.

title: Dungeons and Dayjobs
description: A botched mission leaves the Warriors in debt, so they take day jobs at Slugburger and sling Slugburgers for Witchy Simone!

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Battle for the Bottled City
description: Atom shrinks Superman so he can visit his fellow Kryptonians in the bottled city of Kandor. Soon after, Brainiac attacks and takes off with the bottle. Atom is forced to take control of one of Superman's damaged robots in order to follow after Brainiac and retrieve the city.

title: Moor Fogg
description: Team Tennyson goes international in the Omni-Copter and the first stop is for a hike in the Scottish Highlands, but the weather isn't just bad, it's foggy, and that means one thing and one thing only: the return of The Fogg!

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: The Power
description: Mordecai & Rigby find a mysterious keyboard that allows them to do anything they want, including accidently sending Benson to the moon.

title: Big Trouble for Tiny Miracle
description: Tiny Miracle allows the gang to take advantage of his generosity at the expense of his own health.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Monstra-City/Shut the Pup Up
description: Monstra-city: When all the monsters move from Monster Isle to Townsville, it's up to the Girls to keep the peace./Shut the Pup Up: When the Talking Dog witnesses a crime, he moves in with the girls for protection. But the girls soon realize this chatterbox dog is less than the perfect pet.

title: Bad Bad Cop
description: Vambre and Prohyas pretend to be cops in their attempts to shakedown a dangerous bunch of pirates to find a broccoli smuggler.

title: Grilled Cheese Deluxe
description: Mordecai and Rigby lie about being astronauts in order to cut in line at a restaurant.

title: Free Cake
description: Mordecai and Rigby throw Skips a surprise birthday party in order to get free cake.

title: The Other Fight
description: Eliminated from the Bakugan Battle League, Ajit is airlifted by drone to a massive cargo ship in the middle of Tokyo Bay. Now that he's on board the cargo ship, he must rescue Dan and Drago, and stop whoever is sabotaging the Battle League. Dan and Ajit investigate the mysterious cargo ship that the eliminated brawlers and Bakugan are being held on. Dan races to track down Drago, but along the way runs into a familiar face.

title: Isla Dyer
description: Cuando los ninjas relacionan la desaparición de Jay con Primer Imperio, van a la Isla Dyer para buscar respuestas del diseñador del juego, Milton Dyer.

title: Follow Your Dreams
description: Apple and Onion need to find a dream to follow, so that their lives don't head nowhere.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Manor and Mannerisms
description: Robin attends a ball at Wayne Manor hoping to become heir of the mansion, but will the other Titans spoil his chances?

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: WaterHose-Five
description: The hottest day of the year and a broke air conditioner leads to a water battle of epic proportions to determine who controls the garden hose.

title: Hide and Seek
description: A game of hide and seek uncovers a neglected remnant from Uncle Grandpa's past.

title: Wizz-Ra
description: The ThunderCats freak out when a spooky ghost dressed like a pharaoh appears in their mirrors! They quickly set about to getting rid of every reflective surface in their lair, because that ghost is scary and no one wants to talk to him!

title: Dyer Island
description: When the ninja connect Jay's disappearance to Prime Empire, they set out to Dyer Island to seek answers from the game's designer, the elusive Milton Dyer.

title: Balloon Boys
description: Vic & Val go on a hot air balloon trip with Sal and compete to be his favorite, but things go awry when they try to use the magical Nazca Lines to their advantage.

title: Espias Como Nosotros
description: El tío Andrew le advierte a Axel que su figura de acción "Agente Peligro" está prohibida, isolo para que el juguete escape solo! Axel y el equipo deben devolver a Danger al lugar que le corresponde antes de que el tío Andrew se entere.

title: Frybo
description: Steven helps a Boardie kid with his grueling job by using a magical gem shard that can bring clothing to life.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Sigue la corriente
description: Cuando Sal se queda en lo de Vic y Val, los chicos no lo soportan como compañero, pero finalmente descubren lo genial y mágico que es.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Escape from Monster Island
description: After Bubbles wins two tickets to see the girls' favorite band Sensitive Thugz, Blossom and Buttercup vie for her plus one. But when the Mayor's plane crashes on Monster Island, the girls must put aside their differences to save the day!

title: Te Gustaria Entrar a Primer Imperio?
description: Mientras investigan un robo, los ninjas descubren Primer Imperio, un videojuego que  toma el control de todos los demás videojuegos de Ninjago.

title: Los Rescatadores
description: Cuando un cazador malvado captura a Charlie, Tabes ayuda a los Osos a rescatarlo.

title: Return of Thermometron 9000
description: During a brutal heatwave, Axel and his team must track down Thermometron 9000, stolen by Ice Crusher for two purposes - to keep his hockey rink from melting and to bait the good toys into a rematch!

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Level Thirteen
description: Cyrus Borg discovers a shocking secret about Prime Empire, while the ninja battle an escaped Mechanic in their attempt to reach Level Thirteen and enter the game themselves.

title: Rey del Castillo
description: Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max viajan al Castillo Bishopbrook para visitar a un pariente lejano de la realeza. Pero cuando Ben se encuentra con un "fantasma" en la casa embrujada, resulta ser su nuevo rival, Kevin 11, que lanza a alienígenas aún más retorcidos en su camino: iThornblade, Undertow y Materia Oscura!

title: Cone in 60 Seconds
description: After Owen gets ripped off at the ice cream truck, the kids unite to right that wrong.

title: The Robot
description: Gumball discovers that Bobert is planning to take over his identity and replace him!

title: Shun and Lightning/Premonition of a Storm
description: Shun and Lightning: Shun and Lightning are on the hunt for a rare Tumpee, when they run into McQ! With all the devices related crimes happening in Los Volmos, Shun decides to investigate to try to get to the bottom of McQ's nefarious dealings./Premonition of a Storm: After a run in with McQ, Shun and Lightning find themselves in a little bit trouble. They're trapped!  Tied up with no Bakugan to help them escape, and no one knows their whereabouts. It will take some big help to help them get out of this mess.

title: The Secret
description: Gumball almost loses his mind trying to guess Darwin's secret.

title: Old Lady Bodyguard
description: After being "bought" at a charity auction, Hawkodile is forced to spend the day as Old Lady Edith's personal bodyguard.

title: Esto llega hasta el Once
description: Durante una última parada en una juguetería antes del viaje inaugural de Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max a través del Atlántico, Ben se encuentra con su antiguo bravucón, Kevin 11, que ahora tiene nuevos poderes. Es capaz de transformarse en alienígenas al igual que Ben, como el doble "pirata" de Cannonbolt: iWreckingbolt!

title: Rath of Con
description: Back stateside, Ben can't get into a cat cosplay competition, Top Tail, without a costume of his own; but when he goes Rath, a new cat-like alien with an attitude, Ben's newfound wild side quickly becomes much more than he bargained for.

title: Nivel Trece
description: Cyrus Borg descubre un secreto sobre Primer Imperio y  los ninjas enfrentan al Mecánico que escapó e intenta alcanzar el Nivel 13 para entrar al juego.

title: Los Caza Chicos Malos
description: Izzqy quiere jugar un juego de superhéroes y está dispuesta a hacer lo que sea por ello.

title: Field Trip
description: A group of teenage superheroes are being shown around the Fortress of Solitude when they inadvertently cause the phantom zone projector to trap Superman and release three Kryptonian criminals.

title: Return of the Honeysuckle Rangers
description: Craig discovers that the Honeysuckle Rangers have snuck into his side of the Creek to steal his most prized possession.

title: Inadvertant Inversion
description: As Elliott, Mo and Frankie all try something new at the Hive, they find their worlds are about to be turned upside down again.

title: Grounded
description: Uncle Grandpa must fix his mistake after he helps a grounded teen go to a party.

title: Homeworld Bound
description: Steven heads to the Diamonds for advice on how to control his new powers.

title: Positive Attitude Theory
description: Apple and Onion spend a day in Falafel's shoes and use their positive attitude to prove he shouldn't be so grumpy.

title: The Spoon
description: Gumball and Darwin are unwitting accomplices in a gas station robbery.

title: Tu Eres Rad
description: Cuando K.O. se olvida su chapa identificatoria, Rad le presta la suya, lo cual hace que todos piensen que K.O. es Rad, incluido el mismo Rad.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: El Gran Robo de Bongos
description: Los chicos olvidan conseguir un regalo para Chata en el Día de la Abuela y en un movimiento desesperado, le regalan los bongos que pidieron prestados a Xochi. Sabiendo que deben devolver los tambores, Victor y Valentino fingen ser ladrones para robar los instrumentos.

title: Just Like Robots
description: Axel and the team find themselves bested by Madcap when the baddie uses their digital devices to track their every move in combat, forcing our heroes to act unpredictably.

title: Horn, Sweet Horn
description: Bubbles convinces the Professor to test his new transmogrifying ray on her new friend Donny the Pony in an effort to help him become the unicorn he's always wanted to be. But when it turns Donny into a monster instead, she must stop him before he destroys Townsville!

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: Superstar Rockin' Jay
description: Now inside the Prime Empire game, the ninja find themselves in unfamiliar territory, ignorant of the rules of this world, as they try to find Zane and escape Unagami's army of Red Visors.

title: Special Delivery
description: After being rudely interrupted by Bim Bom during her daily morning song, an angry Unikitty takes the advice of her friends and writes down her feelings into a letter with the intention of keeping the letter to herself, but then accidentally sends it off, complete with postage! The gang then goes on a wild chase through the Unikingdom mail delivery service to keep that rude letter from getting into the hands of Bim Bom, and ultimately hurting her feelings. Turns out, Unikitty's "rude" is everyone else's "nice" and the letter was full of compliments.

title: Green with Envy
description: When the local news interviews Uncle Andrew about his toy inventing, an envious Galileo stages a play in the park with the help of Axel and the team, only to be interrupted by an equally envious Madcap - out to steal the spotlight for himself!

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Teoria de Actitud Positiva
description: Manzana y Cebollín pasan un día en los zapatos de Falafel y usan su actitud positiva para demostrar que no debería estar tan malhumorado.

title: Bye Bye, Bellum
description: The Mayor becomes dependent on the Powerpuff Girls after his assistant Ms. Bellum departs, leaving the girls so busy they accidentally hire the dangerous Bianca Bikini as his new assistant! When Bianca captures the Powerpuff Girls, the Mayor finds the tables turned and must rely on himself to help them.

title: Memories of Bobby
description: When a pillar of the Creek community leaves, our trio mourns their loss by remembering the good times.

title: Keen on Keane/Not So Awesome Blossom
description: Keen on Keane: It's Valentine's Day and the girls notice that Ms. Keane is all alone. Time for a little matchmaking, but who will be the lucky fella?/Not So Awesome Blossom: When Blossom's attack plans fail one after the other, she loses confidence in herself as the group's leader.

title: Sigue Tus Suenos
description: Manzana y Cebollín necesitan encontrar un sueño que perseguir para que sus vidas tengan un rumbo.

title: Time Crimes
description: When Clarence is convinced he has the power to manipulate time he vows to only use his abilities for good. However, a day at school puts his morals to the test when he's given the ultimate choice to help his friends or pause time in the name of fun.

title: The Second Stage Begins/Mechanoids Attack!
description: The Second Stage Begins: With half of the brawlers eliminated, the second stage of the Bakugan Battle league begins. This round will be a timed race to the finish, with all kinds of tricks and traps that will slow down even the best brawlers./Mechanoids Attack!: Mechanoids have crashed the second stage of the Bakugan Battle League, causing all kinds of havoc. The Awesome Brawlers will now have to race against the clock, battling competitors and mechanoids if they want to make it through this round.

title: #TheGreenRoom
description: When Jessica is faced with a Green Lantern Corps disciplinary hearing, Hal appoints himself to be her Peer Advocate.

title: #SobrecargaElectrica
description: Cuando creen que Supergirl ha muerto en una batalla con Livewire, Kara Danvers decide reinventarse con una nueva apariencia, una nueva personalidad y un nuevo nombre: iPower Girl!
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Snake It to the Limit
description: When Seth agrees to let an athletic snake replace his arm so he can finally be good at volleyball, he learns he doesn't need a fancy snake arm to make his teammates happy; he just needs to try.

title: Speechless on the Seine
description: While in Paris, France, Ben catches Zombozo robbing the Louvre, but when Zombozo hypnotizes Ben to remain speechless, Ben must navigate a foreign land like a mime in order to stop the criminal clown and his travelling circus.

title: Tummy Trouble
description: When the Incursean armada kidnaps the Gourmand Queen, Ben and Rook must get the warring Gormand factions to work together to save her and stop the Incursean invasion.

title: Rescue Ranger
description: Tabes helps the Bears rescue Charlie after he gets captured by a villainous game hunter.

title: #ScrambledEggs
description: It's egg-xactly what you think: the home economics "Egg-Baby" assignment, where students are paired up and given an egg to "care for" over a weekend. But when tragedy befalls egg after egg, what should be an easy assignment escalates into a madcap romp with super-high stakes!

title: Convencion de Rath
description: De regreso en casa, Ben no puede inscribirse en un concurso de cosplay de gatos sin su propio disfraz. Pero cuando se convierte en Rath, un nuevo alienígena con aspecto felino y mal carácter, el lado salvaje que Ben acaba de descubrir pronto tendrá resultados inesperados.

title: Scared of Puppets
description: Mao Mao is scared of puppets.

title: Side Effects
description: Ben catches a cold and the symptoms wreak havoc on his alien heroes. To make matters even worse, he has to battle a creature made from cockroaches.

title: Beautopia
description: Susan Strong returns to tell Finn and Jake that her world is in danger!

title: Caffeinated Concert Tickets
description: Mordecai & Rigby make a deal with a Coffee Bean to help them stay awake to work major overtime to pay for concert tickets.

title: Freedom Cactus
description: Clarence draws a comic for the school paper and it becomes a huge hit with the kids. When angry parents step in and censor the comic's crass humor, Clarence must stand up for his artistic vision.

title: Dog Day
description: When a father refuses his daughter's request for a dog, Uncle Grandpa vows to teach the girl responsibility by becoming a dog.

title: #DramaQueen
description: Oliver Queen must face off against his greatest rival yet, Mortimer Drake, while Green Arrow also finds himself up against a new foe, The Cavalier.

title: Champions of Breakfast
description: An epic battle between Vambre and her Waffle Magisword and Prohyas' Pancake Magisword escalates to a war that can only end when Grup solicits his Cave Weirdo pals to be peacemakers.

title: Germ Factory
description: After seeing Leshawna enjoying a sick day at home with ice cream and TV, Duncan convinces the other kids try to get sick too.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Jay Estrella del Rock
description: Dentro de Primer Imperio, los ninjas se encuentran en un territorio desconocido e intentan encontrar a Jay y escapar de los Visores Rojos de Unagami.

title: More Everyone's Tube
description: Through another video browsing session online, we get more videos uploaded by the Bears and their friends.

title: This One Goes to 11
description: During one last stop by a toy store before Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max's maiden voyage across the Atlantic, Ben runs into an old bully, Kevin 11, who now has new powers. He's able to transform into aliens just like Ben, such as the bootleg doppelganger of Cannonbolt. Wreckingbolt!

title: The Alliance
description: As Fourarms, Ben works to thwart an armored truck robbery by a tough female gang leader named Joey, who delivers a disturbing message from Vilgax.

title: Mall-Ra
description: Mumm-Ra builds a mall that's actually a giant labyrinth designed to trap the Thundercats forever. Too bad the Thundercats love the mall so much they could literally spend all eternity there.

title: Fabrica de germenes
description: Después de ver a Leshawna disfrutar de un día enferma en casa con helado y TV, Duncan convence a los otros chicos de que traten de enfermarse.

title: Lucky Girl
description: Ben battles an evil sorcerer whose power whose emanates from mystic charms, one of which turns Gwen into her own superhero named Lucky Girl.

title: Bring on the Bad Guys
description: Axel, Zoe, and the team confront Madcap and his minions as they terrorize a local supermarket.

title: Cy & Beasty
description: Cyborg and Beast Boy can't agree on the better character, Tom or Jerry, so they play a little game of cat and mouse.

title: Del Otro Lado de la Mesa
